title: The Rolling Stones - Stripped Complete (resequenced & expand
description:
When the Stones put out Stripped I thought it was a great idea: do a mostly acoustic album in small clubs and return to the roots instead of doing big stadium shows and overproduced live albums. When the special was aired on MTV I loved it, but upon viewing the DVD release I realized there were several songs that didn't make the TV show or the CD. This torrent rectifies that. It included all the songs from the CD, the DVD and the singles all in one package, and sequenced so it all flows as one album. I hope this entertains you all.
